model_runs.name: cln_nba__scoring_leaders_by_year
model_runs.compiled_code:
WITH
    scorers AS (
        SELECT
            player_id,
            player_name,
            season_year AS year,
            team_initials,
            points,
            RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY team_initials, season_year ORDER BY points DESC) AS rank_by_team_and_year
        FROM `tmc-changemakers-2025`.`csc_dbt_staging`.`stg_nba__player_data`
    )

SELECT
    * EXCEPT(rank_by_team_and_year)
FROM scorers
WHERE rank_by_team_and_year = 1
ORDER BY year, team_initials

model_runs.name: stg_nba__player_data
model_runs.compiled_code:
WITH
    base AS (
        SELECT
        
            CAST(Rk AS INT64) AS rank,
            Player AS player_name,
            Age AS age,
            Pos AS position,
            G AS games_played,
            GS AS games_started,
            MP AS minutes_played,
            FG AS field_goals,
            FGA AS field_goals_attempted,
            `FG%` AS field_goal_percentage,
            `3P` AS three_point_field_goals,
            `3PA` AS three_point_field_goals_attempted,
            `3P%` AS three_point_field_goal_percentage,
            `2P` AS two_point_field_goals,
            `2PA` AS two_point_field_goals_attempted,
            `2P%` AS two_point_field_goal_percentage,
            `eFG%` AS effective_field_goal_percentage,
            FT AS free_throws,
            FTA AS free_throws_attempted,
            `FT%` AS free_throw_percentage,
            ORB AS offensive_rebounds,
            DRB AS defensive_rebounds,
            TRB AS total_rebounds,
            AST AS assists,
            STL AS steals,
            BLK AS blocks,
            TOV AS turnovers,
            PF AS personal_fouls,
            PTS AS points,
            Awards AS awards,
            year AS season_year,
            team_initials AS team_initials,
            _load_timestamp,
            
    DATE(_load_timestamp)
 AS _load_date,
            _transform_timestamp

        FROM `tmc-changemakers-2025`.`csc_dbt_base`.`base_nba__player_data`
    ),

    additional_fields AS (
        SELECT
            *,
            to_hex(md5(cast(coalesce(cast(player_name as string), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_') || '-' || coalesce(cast(season_year as string), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_') || '-' || coalesce(cast(team_initials as string), '_dbt_utils_surrogate_key_null_') as string))) AS player_id
        FROM base
    )

SELECT 
    * 
FROM additional_fields
WHERE player_name != 'Team Totals'

model_runs.name: stg_nba__player_data_incremental
model_runs.compiled_code:
WITH
    source_data AS (
        SELECT
            `rank`,
  `player_name`,
  `age`,
  `position`,
  `games_played`,
  `games_started`,
  `minutes_played`,
  `field_goals`,
  `field_goals_attempted`,
  `field_goal_percentage`,
  `three_point_field_goals`,
  `three_point_field_goals_attempted`,
  `three_point_field_goal_percentage`,
  `two_point_field_goals`,
  `two_point_field_goals_attempted`,
  `two_point_field_goal_percentage`,
  `effective_field_goal_percentage`,
  `free_throws`,
  `free_throws_attempted`,
  `free_throw_percentage`,
  `offensive_rebounds`,
  `defensive_rebounds`,
  `total_rebounds`,
  `assists`,
  `steals`,
  `blocks`,
  `turnovers`,
  `personal_fouls`,
  `points`,
  `awards`,
  `season_year`,
  `team_initials`,
  `_load_timestamp`,
  `_load_date`,
  `_transform_timestamp`,
  `player_id`
        FROM `tmc-changemakers-2025`.`csc_dbt_staging`.`stg_nba__player_data` AS source
        
        /* 
        When a full refresh is running, we'll only pull
        in data from the source table that is newer
        than the most recent record in the target table.
        */
        
        WHERE source._transform_timestamp > (
            SELECT 
                MAX(target._transform_timestamp) 
            FROM `tmc-changemakers-2025`.`csc_dbt_staging`.`stg_nba__player_data_incremental` AS target
        )
        
    )

SELECT * FROM source_data
